&lt;p&gt;May you please provide a PR on GitHub?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Gary&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16850543" author="waldeinburg" created="Wed, 29 May 2019 06:35:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Null would be a valid default value for config (null config is handled by PatternLayout::createPatternParser). To be consistent, I&apos;ll ad an override for the newInstance method on ExtendedThrowablePatternConverter and RootThrowablePatternConverter too.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16870434" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Sun, 23 Jun 2019 04:13:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just to point out the obvious, 2.8.2 was 6 releases ago and was released 2 years ago so this incompatibility break has existed for a while. Not that this shouldn&apos;t be fixed but I would have thought it would have been reported much sooner if it was causing a lot of problems.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
